loginPage.otpinfo: Please enter the code sent to your email
loginPage.SafetyParams1: ACH COLOMBIA S.A., is committed to the security of its clients, wants to provide information and Security recommendations, when using the technological platform in our services:
loginPage.SafetyParams2: 1.Do not create your password with names of relatives, dates of birth, identity document number or address and/or telephone numbers, license plate numbers, etc.
loginPage.SafetyParams3: 2.Do not use the option to store passwords offered by the browser.
loginPage.SafetyParams4: 3.Memorize your username and password and keep them completely confidential. Do not write, share, or lend them.
loginPage.SafetyParams5: 4.Try to change your passwords periodically, or immediately if you suspect that you have lost confidentiality.
loginPage.SafetyParams6: 5.Never provide confidential or personal information (users, passwords, account numbers, etc.) in emails.
loginPage.SafetyParams7: 6.When entering our portals, verify that the website uses encryption (Padlock on the status bar and HTTPS in the address bar, not HTTP, which will always be visible). Validate that the digital certificate is valid and corresponds to ACH COLOMBIA S.A.
loginPage.SafetyParams8: 7.Do not follow links found in emails, instant messages, pop-ups, or banners, which could lead to fake pages.
loginPage.SafetyParams9: 8.Always enter the page by typing the address in the Internet address bar.
loginPage.SafetyParams10: 9.Keep your computer's security tools updated (antivirus, antispyware, firewall, etc.)
loginPage.SafetyParams11: 10.If you have to leave the workstation and you have not finished your session on the portal, lock your workstation (Ctrl + Alt + Del), to prevent other people from taking advantage of that open session and committing fraud to your Name.
loginPage.SafetyParams12: 11.At the end of working on the portal, be sure to log out.
loginPage.SafetyParams13: 12.Do not connect, or log in to unsecured (public) networks, validate that you are connected to a private and reliable network.
loginPage.SafetyParams14: 13.Notify the occurrence of any security event or incident, immediately to the email incidents@achcolombia.com.co that may affect the confidentiality, integrity, and/or confidentiality of ACH Colombia.
